title: 爱丽丝跟着它，然后掉进了地下的一个洞里。
answer: Alice followed it and fell down a hole in the ground.

title: 它正坐在一棵树上,对着大家微笑。
answer: lt was sitting in a tree and smiling at everyone.

title: 有一天，爱丽丝正和她姐姐坐在河边，她看到一只戴着手表的白兔。
answer: One day, Alice was sitting with her sister by the river and she saw a white rabbit with a watch.

title: -它要去哪里?- 去见红桃王后。
answer: And where was it going?To see the Queen of Hearts.

title: 在英国,人人都知道这个故事。
answer: Everyone in Britain knows the story.

title: 她偶尔看一眼姐姐的书。
answer: Once or twice she looked into her sister 's book .

title: 那没有什么好奇怪的。
answer: There was nothing strange about that.

title: 太暗了,她什么也看不见。
answer: lt was too dark for her to see anything..

title: 突然,我家里所有的灯都熄灭了。
answer: Suddenly, all the lights in my house went off.
